# For Comprehensions

```scalascript
val xs = List(1, 2, 3, 4, 5)

val squares = for x <- xs yield x * x
println(squares.mkString(", "))

val evens = for x <- xs if x % 2 == 0 yield x
println(evens.mkString(", "))

val pairs = for
  x <- List(1, 2, 3)
  y <- List(10, 20)
yield x * y
println(pairs.mkString(", "))

for x <- xs if x > 3 do println(x)
```
